('App\\Models\\Blog', 1, 'en', 'title', 'Boost Your Immunity: Essential Vitamins and Supplements You Need'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 1, 'en', 'description', 'A strong immune system is crucial for fighting infections and staying healthy. Vitamins such as C, D, and E, along with minerals like zinc and iron, play key roles in supporting immunity. Vitamin C, found in citrus fruits, helps the body produce white blood cells that defend against infections. Vitamin D, obtained from sunlight and fortified foods, strengthens immune response and is also essential for bone health. Zinc supports immune cell function and wound healing, making it especially important during cold and flu season. Alongside supplements, a balanced diet rich in vegetables, fruits, nuts, and lean proteins is essential. Adequate hydration and quality sleep also contribute to overall immune health. Managing stress through practices like meditation or yoga can further improve immune function. By focusing on these nutrients and healthy habits, you can build a stronger defense against illness.'),
