('App\\Models\\Blog', 3, 'en', 'title', 'Smart Grocery Shopping: Save Money and Reduce Waste'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 3, 'en', 'description', 'Grocery shopping can get expensive when it is not planned well. The key to saving money is creating a well-prepared shopping list based on a weekly meal plan. Buying in bulk and choosing seasonal produce can reduce costs while giving you fresher ingredients. Another smart tip is to stick to your list and avoid shopping while hungry, which helps prevent impulse purchases. Understanding date labels and using proper storage techniques also reduces food waste. Many people throw away perfectly good food because they confuse “best before” dates with “use by” dates. Tracking discount stores, loyalty programs, and digital coupons can further increase savings. By applying these strategies, you can lower your spending and make more sustainable choices.'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 3, 'en', 'meta_title', 'Smart Grocery Shopping'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 3, 'en', 'meta_description', 'Grocery shopping becomes costly without planning—learn how to save and waste less.'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 3, 'en', 'meta_keywords', 'Grocery, Shopping, Savings, Smart'),

('App\\Models\\Blog', 4, 'en', 'title', 'Must-Have Makeup Products for Every Skin Type'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 4, 'en', 'description', 'Choosing the right makeup products supports healthy skin while enhancing your natural beauty. Oily skin benefits from matte foundations and oil-free primers that control shine and help prevent clogged pores. Dry skin does best with hydrating foundations and creamy concealers that provide moisture and coverage. For combination skin, balance is key—lightweight foundations that control oil in the T-zone while keeping other areas comfortable work well. Sensitive skin often needs fragrance-free, hypoallergenic formulas to reduce irritation. A good setting spray helps makeup last all day regardless of skin type. Multi-purpose products like BB creams or tinted moisturizers can simplify your routine while offering skincare benefits. Keeping makeup brushes clean is also important to prevent bacteria buildup and breakouts. Finding products that match your skin’s needs can make a noticeable difference in your everyday makeup routine.'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 4, 'en', 'meta_title', 'Must-Have Makeup for Every Skin Type'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 4, 'en', 'meta_description', 'The right makeup choices can protect skin health and enhance natural beauty.'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 4, 'en', 'meta_keywords', 'Beauty, Makeup'),

('App\\Models\\Blog', 5, 'en', 'title', 'Wardrobe Essentials: Must-Have Fashion Staples for Every Season'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 5, 'en', 'description', 'A well-organized wardrobe is built around timeless pieces that can be styled for many occasions. A classic white shirt is a must-have; pair it with jeans for a casual look or tailored trousers for a more formal style. Well-fitting denim offers year-round comfort and versatility. A little black dress is ideal for evening events, while a well-cut blazer instantly elevates almost any outfit. Comfortable sneakers and elegant heels provide options for both casual and dressy combinations. Accessories like a statement bag and a quality belt can upgrade your look in seconds. Investing in durable basics instead of fast fashion often brings better longevity and sustainability. With these wardrobe essentials, you will always have stylish choices no matter the season.'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 5, 'en', 'meta_title', 'Wardrobe Essentials'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 5, 'en', 'meta_description', 'How to build a timeless wardrobe with versatile staples for every season.'),
