('App\\Models\\Blog', 6, 'en', 'title', 'Small Space, Big Impact: Smart Furniture Choices for Compact Homes'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 6, 'en', 'description', 'Living in a small space does not mean you have to sacrifice style or functionality. Multi-purpose furniture such as sofa beds and foldable dining tables maximizes space while maintaining comfort. Wall-mounted shelves and vertical storage solutions reduce clutter and save floor area. Mirrors reflect natural light and can make a room feel larger. Light-colored walls and furniture also enhance the sense of openness. Compact pieces with hidden storage—like ottomans—help keep things organized. Minimal decor prevents spaces from feeling crowded. Techniques such as under-bed storage and hanging organizers help you use every inch efficiently. With smart furniture choices, even the smallest home can be stylish and practical.'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 6, 'en', 'meta_title', 'Smart Furniture for Small Spaces'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 6, 'en', 'meta_description', 'Practical furniture ideas to make compact homes feel larger and more functional.'),
