('App\\Models\\Blog', 7, 'en', 'title', 'Essential Pet Care Tips: Keep Your Pets Healthy and Happy'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 7, 'en', 'description', '<p>Owning a pet is a big responsibility, and proper care is essential for their well-being. A balanced diet suited to your pet’s breed and size helps ensure they get the nutrients they need. Regular veterinary checkups help detect health issues early and keep vaccinations up to date. Exercise and playtime are crucial for preventing obesity and behavior problems. Grooming routines such as brushing, nail trimming, and ear cleaning keep pets comfortable and reduce the risk of infections. Providing a cozy bed and safe toys creates a comfortable living space and helps pets feel secure and engaged. Socializing with other animals and people improves behavior and reduces anxiety. Training with positive reinforcement strengthens the bond between pet and owner. By following these essential care tips, you can support your furry friends in living a happy and healthy life.</p>'),
('App\\Models\\Blog', 7, 'en', 'meta_title', 'Essential Pet Care Tips'),
